data.description: Come see this beautiful 2 story condo that offers three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and one half bath. Master bedroom features two closets, along with your own person full bath in the master bedroom. Kitchen has full pantry, walk in laundry room, lots of cabinet space with access right into back yard area. The back yard features covered hot tub that stays with the condo, along with side walk to go right into two car garage plus street parking. A monthly HOA fee covers lawn mowing, garbage collection and snow removal. There are also two beautiful ponds with fountains as you enter the neighborhood.
